Title: Things to do in Bukit Timah area
Content: 1. Climb Bukit Timah Hill. 2. Enjoy Indian Muslim food at Al-Azar. 3. Hike and enjoy the lake at Bukit Batok nature park.

Title: Catching a bus to the Downtown line from Southaven 2.
Content: Take any bus with the number 7 in the bus number heading from old Bukit Timah Fire Station towards Beauty World then stop at Beauty World MRT Station.
